{"tid":1049904,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)第1 2 3 4滴血","createTime":"2019-03-06T15:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T21:05:20.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e44d128b4111b7f8d6d605b9533c88aacf6d0a","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=a5dbb6c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=33e4fb5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=5edfe0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/First_blood_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F89%2FFirst_blood_ver1.jpg&h=4f09111d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.約翰&middot;藍波（John Rambo）是一名從越南戰場歸來的美國陸軍綠扁帽退役隊員，回國後，他想尋找以前的戰友。結果卻發現戰友因為接觸橙劑致癌而早已去世。對於沒有親人沒有家庭的藍波來說，戰友的去世讓他十分寂寞和消沉。當他漫無目的地在公路上徘徊時，當地的警察前來盤問。他回答說自己正打算去市區找一家餐館，但是警長將他帶到城外，他因此反抗性的走向城內。於是，維護地區治安的警察便以此把藍波帶回了警局....<br />\n<br />\n2.這回藍波被派返回越南調查越戰失踪軍人下落,看看他們是否已成戰俘。豈料,當藍波到達該地後,突然失去了所有的軍備器材,只剩下一把刀及一套弓箭。後來他發現了真相-他被自己的部隊出賣。在一名越南少女相助之下,藍波發揮堅強意誌及高度求生技巧,克服了一切逆境,並展開了他的複仇計畫,向出賣他的人還以顏色&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.歷經無數戰火與生死考驗，主人公，豪情勇士約翰&middot;蘭博放下手中的殺人武器，在泰國過起了平靜的修行生活。有一天，特勞特曼上校突然出現在他面前。此前不久，上校受命率部隊前往阿富汗，協助當地的聖戰勇士反抗蘇聯人的入侵。雖然在上校給的照片中，阿富汗平民飽受外敵侵略和蹂躪的情景觸目驚心，但蘭博還是拒絕了上校的邀請。某晚，特勞特曼的部隊在執行任務途中遭到蘇聯軍隊的伏擊，其本人也不幸淪為階下囚。得知這一消息，蘭博再也無法靜觀其變。浴血戰士重披戰甲，隻身闖入充滿凶險的阿富汗腹地，展開一場緊張紛呈的絕命營救&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n4.藍波在越戰和阿富汗戰爭之後，因為對美國生活絕望，於泰緬邊界過著與世無爭、靠捕蛇販賣為生的歸隱生活。某日總部設於科羅拉多州的泛亞洲牧師團（Pan-Asian Ministry）的一群義工來請藍波幫忙作船夫帶路，好讓義工能供給河川上游的克倫族人藥品、醫療、祈禱書及補給品。早就看穿世事的藍波以「沒有武器就沒有改變」為由拒絕，但是最終被義工莎拉&middot;米勒（Sarah Miller）說服。牧師團一行人在渡河過程中遭遇水匪，藍波為了保護莎拉不得不出手冷血的將匪徒集體擊斃，但是卻遭到了牧師團領隊麥可&middot;伯奈特（Michael Burnett）的敵視而被拒絕雇用......<br />\n<br />\n11 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=400afbcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=f6338172\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b79a64e0536ba8e16588165a547bf13e1f22587","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d12fdb3d19b8f0209d426e986218f7eb714849","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f61c9d5b2141ab92f996438f0922212cb26c46","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b60f2e1210c7b0bf7e735c0c01e33e5da2e503","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T18:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7365794cc791ccf995764e64bf744ff7ac7651","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0734ff3426bb7db0d16d4b370b7c0bee40609772","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T20:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dbd39819dfb1d628e6d61aec919144fa0991da","tid":1049904,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T21:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}